  "translations": {
    "en": "He prohibited visiting fortune-tellers, and said: 'Whoever visits one and believes him has dissociated from what Allah revealed to Muhammad (peace be upon him and his family).' He prohibited playing with dice, chess, drums, tambourines, and ouds. He prohibited backbiting and listening to it. He prohibited gossiping and listening to it. He said: 'A gossiper will not enter Paradise.'",
